      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">ג׳ונגל, חופים, מקדשים ושקיעות — באלי מחכה לכם</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/plan" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 hover:from-amber-400 hover:to-amber-500 text-black px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/25">
